---
title: Honey-Thyme Chicken & Roast Veggie Toss with Feta & Garlic Aioli
description: A classic combination of honey and mustard never goes amiss. We love the way these flavours caramelise in the pan, giving a crispy, sticky finish. The tender chicken breast is packed with fantastic flavour and complements the bed of delicious roast veggies. Dig in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-veggie-feta-bake-e942e79c.jpg
